title: The List with Colleen Lopez 09.07.2017 - 10 PM
description:
Amy Morrison is our special host this week and she's sharing with us the must-haves for fall, featuring Serena Williams, Vince Camuto, Steve Madden, and more! The List takes the guesswork out of style by showcasing her weekly favorites.
